nodes.text: Grand Admiral Thrawn: A Star Wars Rebels Cinestory Comic

Grand Admiral Thrawn: A Star Wars Rebels Cinestory Comic was a comic book from Joe Books Ltd that would have adapted selected episodes from the Star Wars Rebels animated television series featuring Grand Admiral Thrawn. It was intended to be released on March 26, 2019. Joe Books filed for bankruptcy in April 2019 and the comic book was never released.

Follow one of the most iconic villains in Star Wars history, Grand Admiral Thrawn, in his attempts to destroy the growing Rebellion in Joe Books's cinestory comic adaptation of selected episodes of Star Wars Rebels.
